    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Sports Editor:</p>
        <p>One had to love ''Aggressive, Infuriating and Successful'' (June 5) about Bill Laimbeer and the Detroit Shock. Isiah Thomas was probably right when he told Chuck Daly, ''I should have hired Laimbeer; he's so thick-skinned.'' I believe the Knicks would succeed with Laimbeer.</p>
        <p>Steve Lurie  Tucson</p>
      </block>
